<plot>Allan Peterson has everything that he ever hoped for - His wife Annabel, and a home to call their own. One day, John, the previous owner, comes by for a visit that propels Allan to experience a horrific nightmare that revels that Allan and Annabel have been in their new house before - in a past life. The couple is the reincarnation of John's first wife Madeline and their best friend Peter. Patrick had found out that his wife and best friend were having an affair, thus propelling Patrick to take murderous revenge. In the present, will Allan and Annabel allow this travesty to go unpunished?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?118469</url></doc>
